        <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-brass-horizontal rounded-full shadow-sm mb-6"></div>

        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Not all artifacts are physical objects you can touch. The <strong>Mag Aonghusa/McGennis coat of arms</strong> is an artifact of a different kind—a symbolic representation of family identity that has been preserved and transmitted across centuries.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 my-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-md">
